{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "All these features make it easier to achieve a basic level of PL and thus create a more engaging and effective educational experience.",
    "While the study reveals that ChatGPT can effectively respond to learner inquiries and provide tailored answers, it lacks the advanced capabilities necessary for higher levels of PL (Avramovic & Avramovic, 2024).",
    "Specifically, the bot does not yet possess the ability to create dynamic learning profiles for individual learners or to select appropriate pedagogical strategies that emulate the Zone of Proximal Development (ZPD) necessary for more sophisticated learning (Ferguson et al., 2022).",
    "Achieving these advanced levels of PL requires a deeper understanding of each learner's cognitive and emotional states, alongside the capacity to dynamically adjust teaching strategies (Bai et al., 2023).",
    "The findings suggest that to fully realize the potential of PL, future iterations of ChatGPT must incorporate advanced features such as persistent learner modeling, emotional modeling, real-time assessment, and adaptive pedagogical strategies."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
